                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320517-9-off54 t18320517-9-cd55"></join>, at St. Leonard, Shoreditch, and stealing therein 1 shawl, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320517-9-victim274" type="victimName">
                           Hannah 
                           Brewer
                        <interp inst="t18320517-9-victim274" type="surname" value="Brewer"></interp>
